# Unity Conventions

- Unity 6.x; WebGL target; reuse `unity/shared_bridge/` — no duplicate bridge per game
- Portrait (1080×1920) or landscape (1920×1080) per game configuration
- Protocol version changes require coordinated Flutter and bridge updates
- Unity calculates score/timer; does not assign official ranks or medals
- No Firebase Admin credentials in Unity projects
- Do not commit Library/, Temp/, Builds/, UserSettings/
